e line-by-line in detail with you so you can gain the confidence that we hav=
e captured everything.</span><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">When we go through t=
he scope together =E2=80=93 we can consider adding anything further that is n=
ecessary if we need to. I am exceptionally confident that Stephen and I will=
 capture everything on the first draft =E2=80=93
 but I want you to know that you will sign-off on the scope-of-works as bein=
g complete before we move to the repair phase.</span><o:p></o:p></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">You do not need to j=
oin us for today=E2=80=99s visit =E2=80=93 but you are more than welcome to i=
f you wish. As I stated =E2=80=93 we can review it together once complete. I=
 will let you decide whether you wish to join us or not.</span><o:p></o:p></=
p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Please do not hesita=
te to contact me if you have any questions or concerns at all.</span><o:p></=
o:p></p>
